metadata.name: ESSENCE I
metadata.description:
This piece shows what is real to the eyes and the unseen ultimate Essence of man.
- The light bulbs indicate how bright we shine even in darkness. harness your truth and let your Essence shine.

- The bandages show how hurt we all are and scared of showing or owning who we truly are.

In the end we all Shinee regardless.

My art is subjective to differnt point of views and beliefs & here i'll let you tell your own story.
